                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Combs</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Lima</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-07-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 29, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The President’s message to Congress yesterday refers to Washington protocol as in
                    harmony with mediation, and declares absolute confidence in mediator. I have no
                    doubt new cabinet when formed will accept protocol.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Combs.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
